Financial Account Management Standard Objects
You can use Financial Account and related objects without installing the Financial Services Cloud managed package. Enable the setting to start using the Financial Account and related standard objects.

Deliver Excellent Banking Service with the Retail Banking Console App
Empower bankers and CSRs with access to customer financial account information.
Streamline Communication and Foster Customer Success with the Wealth Management Console App
Model client interaction and service management for wealth managers.
Manage Your Commercial Banking Activities Efficiently with the Commercial Banking Console App
Commercial bankers can manage complex customer requirements, compliance issues, and the competitive landscape.

Get Customer’s Financial Account Information with Standard Objects
Work with financial account FlexCard components to gain more control and flexibility.
Add Flexibility to Financial Accounts in Service Processes with Standard Objects
Use financial account information in OmniScripts of prebuilt service processes to gain more control and flexibility.
